    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1851470/extras/21048bd2fb8a9ef36f7d0d0fce0da45d.avif?t=1769842281\" width=1560 height=336 /></span>After slaying a dragon, <strong>Ikkarus</strong> returns to his village expecting glory, only to receive an unexpected “reward”: a <strong>run-down tavern</strong>, along with a debt of <strong>50,000 gold coins</strong>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >What would enrage anyone else becomes a personal challenge. Determined to prove he is a true hero, Ikkarus decides to rebuild the place, manage the business, and show the man who gave him this “gift” that he made the right choice.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Along the way, he meets <strong>three men</strong> who can help him on this new journey, and maybe even steal his heart.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Follow Ikkarus in this <strong>yaoi slice-of-life</strong> about mixing drinks, dealing with peculiar bartenders, and hunting adorable monsters.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1851470/extras/64ee5597bea113ab297c3a9c956a8012.avif?t=1769842281\" width=1560 height=80 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1851470/extras/1b4f99eb4a9ee7a795a1dd367228e7ef.avif?t=1769842281\" width=1560 height=2734 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1851470/extras/dfcaa506a78fa29b245755e521d2926c.avif?t=1769842281\" width=1560 height=80 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1851470/extras/2096664d8278dec718c5a5e85e39937f.webp?t=1769842281\" width=17 height=18 /></span>Over <strong>5 hours of gameplay</strong>;</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1851470/extras/2096664d8278dec718c5a5e85e39937f.webp?t=1769842281\" width=17 height=18 /></span><strong>3 romance options</strong> (an orc, a demon, and a human);</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1851470/extras/2096664d8278dec718c5a5e85e39937f.webp?t=1769842281\" width=17 height=18 /></span><strong>6 different endings</strong> (one good and one bad for each partner);</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1851470/extras/2096664d8278dec718c5a5e85e39937f.webp?t=1769842281\" width=17 height=18 /></span><strong>13 illustrated CGs</strong>;</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1851470/extras/2096664d8278dec718c5a5e85e39937f.webp?t=1769842281\" width=17 height=18 /></span>Difficulty selection, including an easy mode for visual novel–focused players;</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1851470/extras/2096664d8278dec718c5a5e85e39937f.webp?t=1769842281\" width=17 height=18 /></span>Side quests.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1851470/extras/3e9b4f2b190f02213962c842afa5420c.avif?t=1769842281\" width=1560 height=80 /></span>Yaoi, BxB, Visual Novel, Dating Sim, Romance, Amare, Comedy </p>",
